<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18877989-people-who-eat-darkness"><img alt="People Who Eat Darkness: The True Story of a Young Woman Who Vanished from the Streets of Tokyo--and the Evil That Swallowed Her Up" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1385049880l/18877989._SX98_.jpg" />
